data.description: Welcome to your perfect blend of convenience and comfort in this spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bath concrete block home. Nestled in a prime location, just a stone's throw away from Coastal Community College and minutes from Interstate 95, this property offers an ideal living experience for families and professionals alike. Step inside to discover an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly integrates the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The neutral color palette and contemporary finishes create a canvas that's ready for your personal touch. The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern stainless-steel appliances, ample counter space, and sleek cabinetry - a haven for culinary enthusiasts and entertainers. Enjoy casual meals at the breakfast bar or gather around the dining area for more formal occasions. The spacious master bedroom offers a serene retreat, complete with an en-suite bathroom for your convenience. Three additional bedrooms provide flexibility for a growing family, a home office, or a guest room. The second bathroom is strategically located to cater to both residents and guests. A highlight of this home is the screened-in back patio - an oasis of relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. Whether it's sipping your morning coffee or hosting a barbecue, this versatile space allows you to savor the mild coastal climate year-round. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to Interstate 95, connecting you to nearby cities, shopping centers, and entertainment options. With a neatly landscaped front yard and a two-car garage providing ample storage, this home combines practicality with curb appeal. The quiet neighborhood exudes a sense of community, while the convenient location caters to a modern, active lifestyle Don't miss your chance to own this attractive concrete block home in a sought-after area. Embrace coastal living while enjoying easy access to education, transportation, and recreation.
